> Hi Folks,
>
> Even though I'm content with my 1979 poptop Westy, I'd recommend 
> keeping a poptop away from your 1979 Kombi.  After 1974, Westfalia 
> Werke used standard buses and cut most of the top away to make room 
> for the upstairs bed.  You could adapt a pre-74 poptop, but those are 
> only designed to have a small cot underneath them.
